the Polyhedron Intergalactic Conference is about to begin.

Kamogawa was in a festive mood,
but yesterday's accident aboard the Le Garite flagship,
in satellite orbit above Earth, has caused an uproar.

the fact that the incident will not take place for another millennium

it was my decision alone to use the power of the Vox and to resort to force.

20,000 years ago, the people who fled Earth were scattered throughout the Universe.
Today, through a strange twist of fate,
their descendants have returned to this planet and become one again.
To be able to stand here at that historical moment is a truly joyous event for humankind!
Does this mean it is finally over?
No, let us hope it is.
